  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Prepare tender submissions    </p>\n<p>Prepare progress claims   </p>\n<p>Negotiate with clients, suppliers and subcontractors   </p>\n<p>Hire and document contractors and   subcontractors   </p>\n<p>Act as a liaison between clients and site managers/engineers   </p>\n<p>Keep track of construction materials and inventory   </p>\n<p>Prepare payments for suppliers and subcontractors         </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Bachelor’s degree in quantity surveying, construction engineering, finance, or related field   </p>\n<p>Able to analyze financial records and apply data to improve results   </p>\n<p>Able to analyze problems and strategize for better solutions   </p>\n<p>Possess excellent written and oral communication skills   </p>\n<p>Proficient in computer skills and Microsoft Office Suite</p>\n<p>Only Singaporean and Spore PR needs to apply</p>",
